headline: FactSet Earnings Miss Estimates in Q4, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: FDS's fourth-quarter fiscal 2025 earnings fall short of estimates, but revenues rise 6.2% year over year, with solid growth across regions.

headline: Advertising & Marketing Services Stocks Q2 Highlights: Interpublic Group (NYSE:IPG)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at advertising & marketing services stocks, starting with Interpublic Group (NYSE:IPG).
